metadata.name: Soul Mate 1
metadata.description: Liquid Death hereby grants full rights of ownership of one (1) human soul to the current Holder of this NFT pursuant to the original Bill of Sale for One Eternal Human Soul under such conditions that the Holder possesses six (6) or more Murder Head Death Club NFTs or one (1) Super Rare Murder Head Death Club NFT. In accordance with the original contract referenced herein, the original Seller hereby sells, transfers, conveys, assigns and delivers to the Holder, its successors and assigns, to have and to hold forever, all right, title and interest in, to and under the Eternal Soul via the original Purchaser.
